\mathrm{Error}=\sum\limits_{i=1}^n \int_{\frac{i-1}{n}}^{\frac{i}{n}}(f(x)-f(\zeta_i))\mathrm{d}x
\mathrm{Error}\leq \sum\limits_{i=1}^n \int_{\frac{i-1}{n}}^{\frac{i}{n}}|f(x)-f(\zeta_i)|\mathrm{d}x\leq \sum\limits_{i=1}^n \int_{\frac{i-1}{n}}^{\frac{i}{n}}\frac{1}{n}\sup_{x\in [\frac{i-1}{n},\frac{i}{n}]}|f'(x)|\mathrm{d}x\leq\frac{1}{n}\sup_{x\in [0,1]}|f'(x)|.
